Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reset_max_capacitance(25.10)                      reset_max_capacitance(25.10)

Name
       reset_max_capacitance

Syntax
       reset_max_capacitance

       [-help]

       <object_list>

       Resets  maximum  capacitance limit specified (using the the set_max_ca-
       pacitance command) on the objects in the object list. The valid objects
       in the object list are primary ports, clocks, and current design.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       <object_list>
              Specifies the list of ports, modules, and/or clock waveforms for
              which assertions are reset.

Related Information
       set_max_capacitance

